Show
====

   This item allows to select which list is displayed:

  1. the messages list

  2. the replies list

   The keyboard shortcut for this item is the <TAB> key.


@EndNode

@Node "SortItem" "MailArchiver.guide/SortItem"
@Next "SaveItem"
@Prev "ShowItem"
@Toc "Browsing"

Sort by
=======

   This item allows to select the sort field:

@{i}Date@{ui}
     The list will be sorted by date, then by address, and finally by
     subject

@{i}Address@{ui}
     The list will be sorted by address, then by date, and finally by
     subject

@{i}Subject@{ui}
     The list will be sorted by subject, then by date, and finally by
     address


@EndNode

@Node "SaveItem" "MailArchiver.guide/SaveItem"
@Prev "SortItem"
@Toc "Browsing"

Save As...
==========

   This items allows to save the text of the currently selected message
(or reply) to a text file.

   To select the message to save, just click once on the line
describing this message.


@EndNode

